  <data name="An .apkg mixed package is Apkg&apos;s proprietary format that bundles multiple .deb packages and a manifest.xml into a single gzipped tar archive. The server unpacks each .deb, extracts metadata from its control file, and syncs them to their target APT repositories." xml:space="preserve">
    <value>.apkg 混合套件是 Apkg 的專屬格式，將多個 .deb 套件與 manifest.xml 打包成單一 gzipped tar 封存檔。伺服器會解壓每個 .deb，從其控制檔案提取中繼資料，並將它們同步至目標 APT 套件存放庫。</value>
  </data>
